# This repository publishes only the consolidated, shareable skill pack.
#
# Everything else in this working folder — the harness engine, dev scaffolding,
# fixtures, evals, generated artifacts, and per-machine bindings — stays local
# and is never tracked. Only "The Auditorium/" (the eight-skill pack for Claude
# and Codex) and this .gitignore travel to GitHub.

# Ignore everything at the repository root...
/*

# ...except the shareable skill pack and this ignore file itself.
!/.gitignore
!/The Auditorium/

# OS metadata never belongs in the pack, even inside the allowed folder.
The Auditorium/**/.DS_Store
.DS_Store
